Class ECReport

java.lang.Object
  epc.reports.ECReport

public class ECReport
extends java.lang.Object

ECReport represents a single report within an event cycle.

reportName

private java.lang.String reportName
A copy of the reportName field from the corresponding ECReportSpec within the ECSpec that controlled this event cycle.

groups

private ECReportGroup[] groups
An unordered list containing one element for each group in the report as controlled by the group field of the corresponding ECReportSpec. When no grouping is specified, the groups list just consists of the single default group.
